1. install minibian:
https://minibianpi.wordpress.com/


2. install needed packages
Tested on python 2.7.9

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/29088307/compile-pyaudio-without-jack-without-pulseaudio-etc

apt-get install python-scipy
apt-get install python-pip
apt-get install git
apt-get install alsa-base
apt-get install alsa-utils
apt-get install 
sudo pip install -e git+https://github.com/jameslyons/python_speech_features#egg=python-speech-features
install latest cython version (tested with 0.23.4) http://cython.org/

4. set up alsa

5. clone git repo

6. set up the cython code

7. have fun
